New::SMS::Web
=============

Description
-----------

Net::SMS::Web - a generic module for sending SMS messages using web2sms
gateways. Two subclasses are included:
    - Net::SMS::Mtnsms (http://www.mtnsms.com/)
    - Net::SMS::Genie (http://www.genie.co.uk/)

Prerequisites
-------------

This module requires the following perl modules:

    Carp,
    LWP::UserAgent (1.73+),
    CGI::Enurl     (1.06+),
    URI            (1.09+),
    Term::ReadKey  (2.14+),

It has been tested with perl v5.6.0.

Installation
------------

The usual ...

> perl Makefile.PL
> make
[ > make test ]
> make install

